      "correctIndex": 2,
      "misconceptionFeedback": "⚠️ Gravitational potential energy depends on BOTH mass and height. Since Ep = mgh, at the same height, the heavier object has more GPE. Speed is irrelevant - that affects kinetic energy, not GPE.",
